==Korean==
===Noun===
'''샛별''' (''saesbyeol, saet-'')
#(''literally, "eastern star"'') [[morning star]], [[Phosphorus]]
#* 샛별 지자 종다리 떴다. (''saesbyeol jija jongdari tteossda.'') As the morning star has set, larks have risen.  

====Synonyms====
*[[계명성]] ([[啓明星]], ''gyemyeongseong'') 
*[[명성]] ([[明星]], ''myeongseong'') 
*[[신성]] ([[晨星]], ''sinseong'')   
*[[효성]] ([[曉星]], ''hyoseong'')   

====Antonyms====
*[[개밥바라기]] (''gaebabbaragi'') [[evening star]], [[Hesperus]]

